						<summary>

						<p>This is much damaged. It seems to record an endowment in money for the daily supply of water to the <hi rend="bold">temple of Kanakavīra-Sittaḍigaḷ</hi> by <hi rend="bold">Śembiyaṉ Sembōttilāḍaṉār</hi> son of Viḍēlviḍugu Śombōttilāḍaṉār <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Gaṇaperumāṉār</hi> of Naḍunāḍu.</p>						

